msgid "For example, the вҖңFirst PageвҖқ page style has вҖңDefault Page StyleвҖқ as the next style. To see this, press <switchinline select=\"sys\"><caseinline select=\"MAC\"><keycode>Command+T</keycode></caseinline><defaultinline><keycode>F11</keycode></defaultinline></switchinline> to open the <menuitem>Styles</menuitem> window, click the <menuitem>Page Styles</menuitem> icon, right-click the \"First Page\" entry. Choose <menuitem>Edit Style</menuitem> from the context menu. On the <menuitem>General</menuitem> tab, you can see the вҖңNext styleвҖқ."
